summary: The Joxter from 2009
title: The Joxter from 2009
body:
DeviantArt: https://www.deviantart.com/ajzan-hataru/art/Juksu-119361386

As in the title, I made this picture 10 years ago. This was my vision of the Joxter back then, based on description and some hints from the book, notably color brown, cat’s tail, whiskers and yellowish body parts because of smoking.

Oh, and I didn’t knew how to draw hands properly, so I skipped them awkwardly.

I’m thinking about ramaking this one.
